Introduction

Wooyoung is a South Korean dancer, singer, and songwriter under KQ Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group ATEEZ, in which he debuted on October 24, 2018 with the release of their first mini album "TREASURE EP.1: All to Zero".

Before debuting, Wooyoung appeared and competed on the survival show "MIXNINE" where he was eliminated after ranking 132nd.
